<Author>Sally137
<Content>Great location - Clean and comfortable room Spent 3 nights at the Atlantis. We were very happy with our room. It was clean and the beds were very comfortable. The location was wonderful. We were close to Las Ramblas and to public transportation. The On/Off bus was a few blocks away and it was an easy walk to the Sagrada Familia and the Picasso Museum. With most of the hotels so very expensive, we were delighted to discover the Atlantis for 107 E per night with breakfast and taxes included.*Best dining experience was at Botafumeira. Excellent food, beautiful presentation, and attentive service*Best tapa experience was at La Boqueria. What a fun, fun place that is! 
