<Author>gemandali
<Content>Great city hotel in a perfect location! Just returned from 2 night stay in Hotel atlantis following a 5 night med cruise.Was a little nervous as we had read some rv's that weren't too good.However, we found that the hotel was ideally located at the top of Las Ramblas. The rooms were clean, spacious, fresh towels daily and great facilities.The bar was closed ( don't know why) but we were made very welcome in the neighbouring hotel Lleo.We had our 3 year old son with us and found the Hotel perfect.We were overlooking the courtyard and there was no noise or disturbance.Highly recommend this hotel or if it is booked - try the lovely Hotel Lleo next door. 
