<Author>bobolin
<Content>Enjoyed my stay I stayed here in August 2006 and I was pleasantly surprised by this hotel. It doesn't look like much from the outside but our room was lovely and large. However, I was traveling with my wife and 2 children so we did have a large room. The receptionist told us it was the nicest room in the hotel. Location is perfect near Placa Universidad and steps away from La Ramblas and Placa Catalunia. Metro stop a few metres outsied the hotel also if you need it. We only used the metro when we went to the Marina and the Zoo. Breakfast is adequate. Hot buffet! The usual hotel stuff. I think this hotel must have been recently renovated. I would definetely stay there again. Wifi in the lounge area near the breakfast room. 
